    "body": "Hey @keeyi1chp, sorry for not answering before.\r\n\r\nThat option sets the default gas price for transactions that you send. On the other hand, `getGasPrice` uses the `eth_gasPrice` RPC method which is basically an estimation returned by the node of the current gas price.\r\n\r\nWe don't have a way to set the result of `eth_gasPrice` (we always return a hardcoded value). If by any chance you think that it would be useful to be able to configure it, feel free to open a new issue requesting it.",
