    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I'm going to tentatively close this issue. We have [`hardhat_setNextBlockBaseFeePerGas`](https://hardhat.org/hardhat-network/docs/reference#hardhat_setnextblockbasefeepergas) now which, I think, is what most people would want. This doesn't exactly _set_ the value returned by `eth_gasPrice`, although it does affect it. But that method is not as useful anymore after EIP-1559 and `eth_feeHistory`. If someone really needs some kind of `hardhat_setGasPrice` method, please open a new issue explaining your use case.",
